short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple chrome extension that offers the ability to rerank Twitter feeds by values in post.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows users to rerank their Twitter feeds based on their personal values.
